This software is build upon very popular library: ncurses. 
The main task of program is to allow user select one of
so called "menu items" which are basically just some of
test cases for virtual switch.
Program can be run just by doing:
    1: make
    2: sudo ./demo

After running last command, user will be presented with
a nice menu. Navigation is really straightforward
    1: move upward- press up arrow case
    2: move downward- press down arrow case
    3: select- press enter
    4: quit- press q


